title: S15 Ep55: Monsters and Mysteries of the Mojave w/ M.L. Behrman
itunes:title: Monsters and Mysteries of the Mojave w/ M.L. Behrman
description:
Darkness Radio discuss Monsters & Mysteries of the Mojave with guest M.L. Behrman.

M.L. Behrman is a researcher and author, his canvas is The Mojave and all the wonder, awe and strange phenomena surrounding this mysterious area. We discuss Monsters, Cults, UFO, Alien and other unusual stories.

Get his book here: https://amazon.com


Visit his site here: http://www.mojavemysteries.com/


Check out his YouTube Page: https://bit.ly/2VHfqgh
